title: LiveQuartz 1.7.2
description:
LiveQuartz is a powerful free image editor. It is based on layers and CoreImage filters. You have the layers on the left and the filters on the right of the window. To edit an image, just drag it into the layers&#039; list and it will be added as a new layer. LiveQuartz is localized in English, Chinese, Danish, French, German, Italian, Persian, Russian and Spanish.


Image formats:

pdf,
jpeg,
tiff,
png,
gif,
bmp,
pict,
raw,
...


Image filters:

Distortion Effect,
Geometry Adjustment,
Halftone Effect,
Color Adjustment,
Color Effect,
Tile Effect,
Stylize,
Sharpen,
Blur,
...
